OL,3,CWho is on the Kings Birthday Honours
OL,4,Clist from the midlands?
OL,6,FBlack Sabbath guitarist Tony Iommi has
OL,7,Fsaid it is "unbelievable" to be
OL,8,Frecognised in the King's Birthday
OL,9,FHonours.The 78-year-old musician has
OL,10,Fbeen made a Member of the Order of the
OL,11,FBritish Empire (MBE) in the King's
OL,12,FBirthday Honours for services to music
OL,13,Fand to charity.
OL,15,FIommi is famed for co-founding the
OL,16,Fchart-topping group ` which is widely
OL,17,Fhailed as a pioneer of the heavy metal
OL,18,Fgenre ` in the 1960s alongside the
OL,19,Flate Ozzy Osbourne, Terence "Geezer"
OL,20,FButler and Bill Ward.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@YO]{D@]OU{D@dO]
