OL,3,CWho is on the Kings Birthday Honours
OL,4,Clist from the midlands?
OL,6,FHe has also dedicated himself to
OL,7,Fphilanthropy and is focused
OL,8,Fhumanitarian projects such as
OL,9,Finternational disaster relief, as well
OL,10,Fas cancer advocacy, having been
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with lymphoma in 2012.
OL,13,FIommi said: "What an unbelievable
OL,14,Fhonour to receive an MBE.
OL,16,F"Music has been my life and I've been
OL,17,Fvery lucky to share this journey with
OL,18,Fmany amazing people and fans, and I'm
OL,19,Fvery grateful for all the support
OL,20,Falong the way.
OL,26,@uD@MOUxD@AOU
