OL,3,CWho is on the Kings Birthday Honours
OL,4,Clist from the midlands?
OL,6,F"It's been a privilege doing something
OL,7,FI love and then to see that music
OL,8,Fconnect with so many over the years.
OL,10,F"And, to be able to help raise money
OL,11,Ffor charities close to my heart has
OL,12,Fmeant the world to me."
OL,14,FIn football, six of the European
OL,15,FChampionship-winning Lionesses have
OL,16,Fbeen awarded an MBE for serves to
OL,17,Ffootball, including Birmingham-born
OL,18,Fgoalkeeper Hannah Hampton, and Jess
OL,19,FCarter who's from Warwick.
