OL,3,CWho is on the Kings Birthday Honours
OL,4,Clist from the midlands?
OL,6,FThousands of fans lined the Mall in
OL,7,FJuly to celebrate the Lionesses'
OL,8,Fdramatic victory over Spain.
OL,10,FLee Carsley, England men's Under-21s
OL,11,Fcoach, has also been awarded an MBE
OL,12,Ffor services to football The former
OL,13,Finterim England manager from Solihull
OL,14,Fguided his squad to victory in the
OL,15,FEuropean Under-21 Championship in 2023.
